---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Learn a term correction

Usage: mf term learn [OPTIONS] --original <ORIGINAL> --correct <CORRECT>

Options:
      --original <ORIGINAL>  
      --root <PATH>          
      --config <PATH>        
      --correct <CORRECT>    
      --project <PROJECT>    
  -v, --verbose...           
      --format <FORMAT>      [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
  -q, --quiet                
      --no-color             
  -h, --help                 Print help
  -V, --version              Print version
